{"tid":2234552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡錫進鄭重闢謠 反遭中國網友要求公開財產和子女位置","createTime":"2020-10-08T03:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T14:12:07.000Z","uid":337052,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"45ac88623b8a67681553c38841718a52709c51b5","tid":2234552,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:46:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">胡錫進</span></strong><br />\n今天 01:16 來自 HUAWEI P30 Pro<br />\n<br />\n之前有自媒體造謠說，<span class=\"red\">老胡一年收入1200萬元以上。因為它太離奇，一看就是假的</span>，我未予回應。不曾想，7日蘋果日報通過與海外不嚴肅網站&ldquo;接龍&rdquo;，接過了這個謠言，並且<span class=\"red\">把老胡&ldquo;在加拿大有個兒子&rdquo;的謠言一起重炒一遍</span>。蘋果日報這樣幹太不專業也太沒底線了吧，他們的記者可以打個電話向我求證啊（他們之前為別的事聯繫過我），為何要把這個很明顯的謠言當可靠信息加以報導放大呢？蘋果日報的消息不會都是按照這樣質量標準生產出來的吧？<br />\n<br />\n最近針對老胡的謠言越來越多，我知道，有一些力量恨我，想要用誹謗壓垮我。對陷入這樣的處境，我不抱怨，<span class=\"red\">這大概是我獲得影響力並且將它用於捍衛國家利益必須承受的代價</span>。但我想說，那些力量壓不垮我，哈哈，我說過很多次了：老胡奄奄一息地活著並且長壽。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以通過老胡的遭遇看清當下的輿論場上有多少明槍暗箭，以及它們的背後又有多少狡詐和無情。至於老胡本人，<span class=\"red\">我常對自己說：出來混，就要堅強些，心大些。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7CL9h8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7CL9h8.png&h=e7f20cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eg3b4Ry.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEg3b4Ry.png&h=7b15f358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdnwkpX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdnwkpX.png&h=451b930c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53a163dbe6e26edb70f7c525b6fe52de45bf793e","tid":2234552,"uid":337052,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ztfM46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ztfM46.png&h=43eb2d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLj6TK9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLj6TK9.png&h=6f46b7b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8085ee36e8339a993376144318b0e4539e2162fc","tid":2234552,"uid":77196,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩公開"},{"pid":"cf83b80bb571e7ae4376c757595462014da28d2a","tid":2234552,"uid":114014,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"別讓牠跑掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51aa881349566098fa6dcf8e11c3efccad24c7d","tid":2234552,"uid":117754,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"叫UBS公開, 國外私人銀行中共黨員基本權利黎. <br />\n麻煩平民用返圈內銀行, 方便各地共黨圈返條數."},{"pid":"3611dba3083ac51869f4dd033a769691e01ce553","tid":2234552,"uid":259901,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:56:41.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩公開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf41ba4cbb9b7d0d179b163fb0c9db2c22fff3b","tid":2234552,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e87c7d19a4816722099044e6a74881965f51672","tid":2234552,"uid":153811,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c722c5ff4d719fc0c3b1477b3948f49f97874c02","tid":2234552,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fbb3b74bb42d984dbae56b1bdb2ffc163c89d0","tid":2234552,"uid":169801,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:11:26.000Z","msg":"其實佢係咪高級黑來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解次次係得佢D評論刪得特別慢<img sr